subject: Swimming
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps won the 200-meter individual medley for his 20th over all medal. Tyler Clary, who long has competed in the shadows of his fellow Americans, upset Ryan Lochte in the 200-meter backstroke.
